description:
So I tested positive for longterm Covid antibodies on one of the most accurate blood tests out there. It was not the bogus PCR test which is extremely inaccurate and has a tendency to create many false “positives” but the antibody test. I didn’t want to get the test but I had to unfortunately in order to do an activity which I wished to do after traveling out of state to Sedona. Apparently they said I must have “had” the virus 6-8 weeks ago. I didn’t have so much as a sniffle, I wasn’t sick at all, not a single symptom and the person that I live with, sleep with, eat with and kiss didn’t even catch it from me. 
-
This is what we’ve shut down the world for? This is what we’ve traumatized and masked ourselves and our children for? I pray that we awaken from this slumber and fight peacefully for the vestiges of freedom which we have left.
-
Don’t delude yourself to believe that a magical vaccine will solve this. I currently have IgG, longterm antibodies. I have an actual vaccine created by my immune system floating through my veins and I’m still required to get a temperature check and wear masks to go anywhere. 
-
Mandatory masks. Now replace the word mask with the word vaccine or the word Covipass or the word microchip. 
-
We must stand together in our Divine birthright and with our sacred breath to resist this tyranny. 
-
Where there is God there is no tyranny. 
.
